WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:01.700
Previously on Guilt.

00:01.747 --> 00:02.948
What the hell?

00:02.973 --> 00:04.377
You're under arrest.

00:04.413 --> 00:06.307
Why did Molly have your blood

00:06.332 --> 00:07.436
under her fingernails?

00:07.471 --> 00:08.727
BRUNO: <i>Grace said that Molly thought</i>

00:08.752 --> 00:10.265
<i>someone was watching her,
stealing her things.</i>

00:10.285 --> 00:11.318
<i>Now, Molly's stuffed monkey</i>

00:11.353 --> 00:12.768
<i>has been stolen from the crime scene.</i>

00:12.793 --> 00:14.891
<i>We know the photo had to be
taken from this apartment.</i>

00:14.927 --> 00:16.623
- Do you live alone?
- It's just me

00:16.658 --> 00:18.191
and me little boy.

00:18.226 --> 00:19.259
What do you want?

00:19.294 --> 00:20.660
You keep my secrets,

00:20.696 --> 00:22.262
<i>I'll keep yours.</i>

00:22.297 --> 00:24.230
I need you to get a vial

00:24.266 --> 00:26.266
<i>of Molly Ryan's blood.</i>

00:26.301 --> 00:28.234
- You're off the case?
- Gwen.

00:28.270 --> 00:30.203
<i>She thinks I've got feelings for you.</i>

00:30.238 --> 00:32.639
I like your necklace. I knew
a girl who had one just like it.

00:32.674 --> 00:34.541
The necklace is from a special club,

00:34.576 --> 00:36.509
<i>where anyone with enough money</i>

00:36.545 --> 00:37.610
<i>can have whatever they want.</i>

00:37.646 --> 00:39.512
When I get
my hands on whoever killed her,

00:39.548 --> 00:40.647
I promise you, before they die,

00:40.682 --> 00:42.482
they're going to suffer.

00:43.518 --> 00:46.453
♪ ♪

